oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on pink) announcing the 1st Annual Club Luna Masquerade Party- Halloween Party featuring Diamond Jim and Family Jewels with the Cheeksters and Watermelon Road at Club Luna on October 31.
